    //   Cohesion:    cocycle residual of (T_candidate - T_target) in Z (PRIMARY)
    //   Spectral:    missing values × total_cells (value presence)
    //   Count:       per-value mass imbalance (value conservation)
    //   L1:          sum |derived - target| across all cells (positional refinement)
    //
    // Cohesion is PRIMARY. A rotation that preserves all category relationships
